Setup:
- Create directory
  $ mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
- Clone Vundle
  $ git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim
- Copy the vimrc and gvimrc files to $HOME
  $ cp vimrc ~/.vimrc && cp gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
- Launch VIM and run :PluginInstall 
- Close and relaunch VIM
